des:
Ruff! Bark! Woof woof! grrrrrrrr. What kind of bark do you want to hear? Perk up your ears, because this skill lets you experience all the fun things that our furry four-legged-friends do. 

Better with Screen
See spot bark. See spot jump and play! Get the full experience by using Big Bark on all Alexa devices with a screen, like the Echo Show. 

Share a Bark We want to see and hear your precious pup! Drop us an email at talk2simmba@gmail.com and we might feature it in the skill. You and your dog would be almost famous!
